  <brief_title>Changes in Esophageal Motility and Swallowing Symptoms After Thyroid Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Changes in Esophageal Motility and Swallowing Symptoms After Thyroid Surgery - a Prospective Cohort Study</official_title>
